---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { profile } from "../../data/profile";
---

<BaseLayout title={`Contact · ${profile.name}`}>
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">
        <span data-lang-content="en">Contact</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">联系</span>
      </p>
      <h1>
        <span data-lang-content="en">Where to reach me.</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">联系入口。</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
    <p class="page-lead" data-lang-content="en">Different contexts fit different channels: LinkedIn for business and media, GitHub for open source, X for short-form AI/product updates, and Zhihu for longer Chinese-language discussions.</p>
    <p class="page-lead" data-lang-content="zh">不同事情适合不同入口：商业合作和媒体采访看 LinkedIn，开源和技术讨论看 GitHub，短观点和海外 AI 讨论看 X，中文语境下的长讨论可以在知乎。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>
        <span data-lang-content="en">Channels</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">入口</span>
      </h2>
      <ul class="plain-list">
        <li>
          <a href={profile.links.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a>
          <span data-lang-content="en">Business conversations, media requests, speaking invitations, overseas opportunities, and partnerships.</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">适合商业合作、媒体采访、演讲邀请、海外机会和合作沟通。</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href={profile.links.github}>GitHub</a>
          <span data-lang-content="en">Technical discussion, open-source work, and Memex-related issues, ideas, or pull requests.</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">适合技术讨论、开源协作，以及 Memex 相关 issue、想法和 pull request。</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href={profile.links.x}>X</a>
          <span data-lang-content="en">Short-form thoughts on AI products, open source, agents, and what I am building.</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">适合看一些更短的 AI 产品、开源、Agent 和正在做的事情。</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href={profile.links.zhihu}>Zhihu</a>
          <span data-lang-content="en">Chinese-language conversations around AI products, product thinking, and public writing.</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">适合中文语境里的 AI 产品、产品判断和公开写作讨论。</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>
        <span data-lang-content="en">What I’m open to</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">适合聊的方向</span>
      </h2>
      <ul class="plain-list">
        <li>
          <strong data-lang-content="en">AI applications after the demo stage</strong>
          <strong data-lang-content="zh">从 demo 之后开始的 AI 应用</strong>
          <span data-lang-content="en">Products that need to enter real data, workflows, quality control, distribution, and repeated business use.</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">需要进入真实数据、业务工作流、质量控制、分发和重复使用场景的产品问题。</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong data-lang-content="en">Commercial AI SaaS and creative workflows</strong>
          <strong data-lang-content="zh">商业化 AI SaaS 与创意工作流</strong>
          <span data-lang-content="en">E-commerce media generation, AI commercial photography, global SaaS distribution, and vertical product strategy.</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">电商媒体生成、AI 商拍、全球 SaaS 分发和垂直产品策略。</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong data-lang-content="en">Personal AI, memory, and open source</strong>
          <strong data-lang-content="zh">个人 AI、记忆和开源</strong>
          <span data-lang-content="en">Local-first tools, private context, long-term memory, personal agents, and open-source product growth.</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">Local-first 工具、私人上下文、长期记忆、个人智能体和开源产品增长。</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>
        <span data-lang-content="en">Useful background</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh">联系前可以先看</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="page-copy" data-lang-content="en">These are the shortest paths into my current work and public thinking.</p>
      <p class="page-copy" data-lang-content="zh">想先了解背景，可以从这几个入口开始。</p>
      <div class="link-stack">
        <a href="/works/">
          <span data-lang-content="en">Work</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">作品</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/blog/">
          <span data-lang-content="en">Blog</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">文章</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/events/">
          <span data-lang-content="en">Events and interviews</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">活动与访谈</span>
        </a>
        <a href={profile.links.memex}>Memex</a>
        <a href={profile.links.weshop}>WeShop AI</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
